name: My Abstract Dreams by Mart Biemans

metadata.name: AQUA PAINT
metadata.description:
My Abstract Dreams is a collection of experimental art by Mart Biemans. 

Out of pure passion to create and experiment, the collection has grown into my biggest personal project to date. 

The primary goal of it being to learn new techniques and develop myself as an artist. 

Being an artist can be a struggle, I have experienced this myself. A percentage of the profits will be directly invested into upcoming NFT artists.
